## Part 2 — Pentagon + watchdog activity during run 014's window

Bridge err.log query for window 14:45-14:50 UTC: NO entries.

Reason: per the run 008 diagnostic finding ("the native runner stops/restores the trigger bridge during native runs"), the bridge-side LaunchAgent watchdog from af57375 does NOT log during native-runner activity. The relevant watchdog is the RUNNER-SIDE watchdog embedded in scripts/run-native-pentagon-task.mjs (per the dirty-edits audit in 95d6b31). Its events are written to the per-run log, not the bridge err.log.

